BH hearing Shoko's order, pulls out his pistol, he quickly grabed a 
rabbit from the ground and shot it. he quickly took out a pen a
wrote. 
~Dear Lino,     I am BH and my soilder Blastrage  are bounty hunters. 
We want a real case, like assasination, In hope to hire us you must 
pay us atleast 200 kilos of energon for a regular soilder and 500 
kilos for a leader or sub commander.~ BH toss the bunny in lino's 
direction and runs off back to the .

Blastrage follows BH. Blastrage fires a 6 rockets at the maximal base.
